items.title: Trump says 25% tariffs on Mexico and Canada may not include oil: 'Oil is going to have nothing to do with it as far as I’m concerned'
items.description: The president confirmed his long-threatened tariffs will come into effect on Saturday, and said they “may or may not rise with time.”
